posting_body: ['WE HAVE A RENT TO OWN PROGRAM EASY TO  QUALIFY!', 'Quick move in.', 'If you are an independent worker have low credit or background issues and have problems finding a place to settle with your family, do not hesitate call me or TEXT me, I am a rental expert in South Florida, I will find a property for you and get you approved.', 'WE HAVE A RENT TO OWN PROGRAM with credit score of over 550, we will buy any property CASH for you  up tp $600,000 and then rent it to you for 1 to 3 years until you can get ready to purchase it, it will save some of your rent money towards the purchase ( about 25% of payment).', 'This is it!', 'Resort style living!', 'Enjoy fantastic views of the intracoastal waterways and modern high rises from this beautiful 18th floor unit in a building that is directly on the beach!', 'This spacious apartment has 2 extra large bedrooms, 2 baths, walking closets, open concept dining/living room with bar area perfect to share family memories and live the South Florida lifestyle.', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'I RESPOND INMIDIATELLY!!', 'show contact info', ')', '""EASY SOLUTIONS REALTY LLC ""']
